{
  "stem": "2718.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason why they asked families to stay together was because they wanted to avoid any sort of panic and any sort of unnecessary [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] delay by people going hysteric.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and especially for the children, to stay with their mothers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't care about, really, who was young and who was old as long as they had a sort of an order.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the Germans are well know for order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was they wanted order.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The second command was to leave all their belongings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Put the belongings-- make sure that their belongings are marked, that our names are on it, and leave it where it is.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we will get it-- will get it back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If our name is properly marked, we will get it back after we-- we've been allocated to our quarters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the second command.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, of course, we started with five abreast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We started to march.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We-- we got to the-- to the end of the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Mothers who were holding the children and elderly people, they were sent to the right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people who were-- who were independent and who looked strong enough to-- to work, useful, they were sent to the left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We-- we had no idea because even after we were sent to the left, and people to the right, there was another section where women were separated from men.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first-- the first selection came-- first selection came when the-- the useful from the-- from the liabilities, sort of.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, they never-- they never tried to separate the mother from the child.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
